Sometimes there is an error regarding DB Table which is the hidden table.
The error message shown that "Try to repair db table"
You may follow these steps to repair the db tables:
1. Goto phpmyadmin
2. Choose a database
3. Use sql command
4. Type this command and press Go:
  REPAIR TABLE mysql.db;
  The result will show that mysql.db has been repaired.
5. Do the same for each database
6. Done.
